snippet.title: #Shorts Amber heard
snippet.description:
Today's question is:
Which celebrity do you suspect is pure evil in private?

The most popular answers to todays question include: 
 # Drake

 # Ellen

 # madonna

 # Dr. Phil

 # Kat Von D

 # Elon Musk

 # Tim Allen

 # Tyra Banks

 # Jared leto

 # Tom Cruise

 # Joel Osteen

 # Jeff Bezos.

 # Nicki minaj

 # Demi Lovato

 # Adam Levine

 # Kardashians

 # chris brown

 # Chris Brown

 # Amber Heard

 # Lea Michelle

 # Jefree Starr

 # Kylie Jenner

 # Steve Harvey

 # James Corden

 # Oprah Winfrey

 # Oprah Winfrey

 # Jennifer lopez

 # Michelle Duggar

 # Chrissy Teigen.

 # Gwyneth Paltrow

 # Mark Zuckerberg.

 # Kenneth Copeland

 # Daniel o'Donnell

 # Salmon bhoi(Salman khan)

 # Well clearly Travis Scott

 # Dan get in the van Schneider

 # Bill Cos...... oh, nevermind

 # Does anyone remember onission?

 # All signs point to Amber Heard

 # I think James Corden.

Oh wait-

 # Any celebrity that's in scientology.

 # Pretty much most internet influencers.

 # Idk James Franco gives me weird vibes.

 # Ellen D. Theres something in the eyes.

 # I have a feeling about Harvey weinstein

 # I am here to just read tea about celebrities.

 # Jerry Seinfeld always struck me as a sociopath

 # Betty Whi


Oh sorry, i thought you meant pure angel

 # You guys make me Google shiz that has no place in my Search History.

 # J Lo. I've heard she is super demanding and shitty towards her help.

 # Jimmy Fallon. There is something about his fakeness that triggers me

 # Whats the over/under on how many times Tom Cruise gets mentioned? 30?

 # Machine Gun Kelly and Megan Fox, they give me bad vibes for some reason

 # Lena Dunham. Is she even still a celeb? She just seems like a total asshat

 # Dr. Phil. Porcine beady-eyed sociopath. The sicker they are the more he dives in.

 # Hopefully Ghislaine Maxwell will give us the full list before she "kills herself"...

 # Dhar Mann. I'm aware he's not quite a celebrity, but still. Something's really off about him.

 # I 100% believe Tom Cruise is a serial killer and Scientology provides him his victims and covers it up.

 # Gwyneth Paltrow, because of her goop products that are actually bad for health and she is still promoting them to people.

 # Arnie Hammer is allegedly a cannibal. 

Which must have made failing the audition for the role of Hannibal Lecter particularly disappointing.
